column1: Seasonally adjusted civilian unemployment rates AS ORIGINALLY PUBLISHED, monthly 1957-present
NOTE:  The seasonally adjusted unemployment rate was first published for June 1957.  Beginning with data for January 1967,
data refer to persons 16 years and over; data for earlier periods refer to persons 14 years and over.
Over-the-month change in seasonally adjusted unemployment rate as originally published, 1957-present
WARNING:  The December over-the-month change shown here is calculated from the orginal November value and does not refect the
"as published" change shown in the December news release, which is based on a revised seasonally adjusted November estimate.
NOTE:  The seasonally adjusted unemployment rate was first published for June 1957.  Beginning with data for January 1967,
data refer to persons 16 years and over; data for earlier periods refer to persons 14 years and over.
